To bring

a small notebook and a pen;
a camera or phone to take notes and/or pictures;
your personal laptop, if possible;
comfortable shoes: we will do a fair amount of walking;
Travel adaptors can be easily purchased at the Gardens Shopping Centre;
We recommend that participants purchase a local sim card with a small data plan upon their arrival at Cape Town airport, from companies such as MTN or Vodafone. They are located immediately after the gate for international arrivals, on the right. This will facilitate communication and fieldwork during the masterclass.

Miscellaneous

Bring a small notebook and a pen, a camera or phone to take notes and/or pictures, your personal laptop, if possible;
Take comfortable shoes: we will do a fair amount of walking;
Travel adaptors can be easily purchased at the Gardens Shopping Centre next to the Guest House ;
We recommend that participants purchase a South African sim card with a small data plan upon their arrival at Cape Town airport, from companies such as MTN or Vodafone. Shops are located immediately at the exit of international arrivals, on the right-hand side. This will facilitate communication and fieldwork during the masterclass.
